  "title": "Microsoft Threat Intelligence Center - MSTIC",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode we interview Pete Bryan \n               (\n                  <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/peter-bryan-77588473/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                  <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://twitter.com/MSSPete'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-x-twitter\"></i></a>\n               ) \n               from the Microsoft Threat Intelligence Center - MSTIC - about lessons learned from the recent highly-public nation-state attacks on US infrastructure.\n\n               <br><br>\n                We also cover security news about GitHub, Azure Sentinel and Monitor, CosmosDB, Storage Accounts, Azure Functions, SimuLand, Gladys also announces that there is now a Spanish edition of the Azure Security Podcast.\n\n               <br><br>\n               <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/219557?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"rss embed thingy\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/248603/\">TTTTTT | RSS.com Podcasting</a></iframe>\n               <h5>Links</h5> \n               <ul>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/219557/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-pencil\"></i></a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://azsecuritypodcast.net/es'>The Spanish Azure Security Podcast</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/ab-tls-upgrade/'>Azure Backup: Upgrade to TLS 1.2 or above for secure MARS agent backups by September 1, 2021</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/key-rotation-and-expiration-policies-for-azure-storage/'>Key Rotation and Expiration Policies for Azure Storage</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/now-available-pricing-changes-to-azure-sentinel-and-azure-monitor-to-help-you-reduce-costs/'>Pricing changes to Azure Sentinel and Azure Monitor to help you reduce costs</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/public-preview-identitybased-connections-in-azure-functions-with-latest-azure-sdk-triggers-and-bindings/'>Identity-based connections in Azure Functions with latest Azure SDK triggers and bindings</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/asc-may2021-2/'>Azure Security Center: Public preview updates for May 2021</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/asc-may2021-1/'>Azure Security Center: General availability updates for May 2021</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/github-integration-with-azure-security-center-now-in-public-preview/'>Azure Security Center integration with GitHub Actions, in public preview</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/azure-developer-community-blog/kickstart-collaborative-devsecops-practices-with-github-and/ba-p/2357730'>Kickstart collaborative DevSecOps practices with GitHub and Azure</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/cosmos-db/how-to-always-encrypted?tabs=dotnet'>Use client-side encryption with Always Encrypted for Azure Cosmos DB (Preview)</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://michaelhowardsecure.blog/2021/06/03/my-list-of-security-announcements-from-build-2021/'>My List of Security Announcements from Build 2021</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/conditional-access/concept-condition-filters-for-devices'>Conditional Access: Filters for devices (preview)</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.microsoft.com/security/blog/2021/03/02/hafnium-targeting-exchange-servers/'>HAFNIUM targeting Exchange Servers with 0-day exploits</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.microsoft.com/security/blog/2021/03/04/goldmax-goldfinder-sibot-analyzing-nobelium-malware/'>GoldMax, GoldFinder, and Sibot: Analyzing NOBELIUM’s layered persistence</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.microsoft.com/security/blog/2021/05/27/new-sophisticated-email-based-attack-from-nobelium/'>New sophisticated email-based attack from NOBELIUM</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://github.com/microsoft/msticpy'>MSTICPy</a></li>\n               </ul>"
